      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>to a large baking tray (or two) and sprinkle with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tsp [1 1/2 tsp] [2 tsp] <strong>sugar</strong> and a large drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then put the tray[s] in the oven for 8-10 min or until crispy – this is your <strong>crispy 'seaweed'</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
