    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are caramelising, slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways and scoop out the seeds with a spoon then slice into matchsticks, discard the seeds</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> lengthways into batons</p>",
