    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have caramelised, divide the mixture evenly between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>sticky hoisin sauce</strong>, pack with <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong>,<strong> spring onion batons </strong>and garnish with<strong> crispy 'seaweed' </strong>and<strong> crispy onions </strong>– these are your <strong>pulled hoisin mushroom & crispy 'seaweed' wraps</strong></p>",
